snippet.textDisplay: The fires in Australia ARE  NOT DUE TO CLIMATE CHANGE they are due to Government NOT managing our land. The Australian bush land MUST be burnt of every couple of years to remove the leaf litter on the ground that builds up and this has not been done for decades. The burn off allows plants to germinate and grow. This is a requirement as our plants have had this happen for 40,000 years of aboriginal management and it must happen for the health of the system.. When this is not done the result is this catastrophic event. Politicians and fire services should go to jail for this. As I said, this is not climate change but bad Government.
